data.description: Northwest schools, primary on main, 3bdrm/2.5bath, 2 car garage in Summerfield, on a 1.12 ac lot. Den & bonus room in basement can be used as flex rooms with multiple uses, office and/or exercise area. Den currently being used as a music/piano studio. Den has fireplace & exterior door for private entry, also has 1/2 bath. Upstairs hall bathroom has been renovated, tile in bathtub, floors, & vanity has been replaced, as well as fixtures. Barn door to laundry/kitchen area and also to primary bathroom. Spacious closets in all bdrms. Water treatment system & tankless water heater. Deck boards have been replaced. Large fire pit area in the backyard. Storage building. HVAC 2021, roof 2019, some windows have been replaced as per seller. Floors on main and basement have been replaced. Seamless gutters at dettached garage. Exterior recently painted. House is located on dead end, low traffic street, private setting. NO HOA. Seller offering $1900 credit towards flooring and garage door panel.
